_sText:
This map is a remix of ( i found very cool map ) cs_bloodstrike (1.6) i've made it with a Dust theme and hopefully u'll enjoy playing it, this is my 1st post and this my second map i made with hammer editor.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Fast map details: This map is pritty small and it requires aiming skills. i recommend you to play this map with not to much people but there are around 24 spawn points in the map.

BTW i called it CS_bloodstrike_dust cuz that was the original name, but it isnt a cs map.                                                                                    

if you could give me advice on how to improve my map then please post a comment , thanks
